    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA93-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu varaivu kaṭāyatu. (ET: pakaṟkuṟi.)</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how marriage is asked for.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA93">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            piracan tūṅkap perumpaḻan tuṇara</l>
<l>            varaiveḷ ḷaruvi mālaiyi ṉiḻitarak</l>
<l>            kūla mellām pulampuka nāḷu</l>
<l>            mallaṟ ṟammavim malaikeḻu veṟpeṉap</l>
<l>            pirintō riraṅkum peruṅka ṉāṭa </l>
<l>            celka meḻumō ciṟakkaniṉ ṉūḻi</l>
<l>            maruṅku maṟaitta tiruntiḻaip paṇaittō</l>
<l>            ṇalkūr nucuppiṉ melliyaṟ kuṟumakaḷ</l>
<l>            pūṇṭā ḻāka nāṇaṭa varuntiya</l>
<l>            paḻaṅkaṇ māmaiyu muṭaiya taḻaṅkukuraṉ </l>
<l>            mayirkkaṇ muraci ṉōrum</l>
<l>            muyirkkuṟi yetirppaip peṟalaruṅ kuraittē.</l>
        </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from the land of big stones, where those separated are aggrieved:</l>
<l rend="indent2">“when the honeycombs are hanging, when big fruits are clustering,</l>
<l rend="indent2">when white waterfalls tumble down from the mountain in the evening,</l>
<l rend="indent4">when all the grains enter the fields daily,</l>
<l rend="indent3">abundance has, alas, this mountainous region”<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">malaikeḻu veṟpu</term>: if <term xml:lang="ta">veṟpu</term> can have <term xml:lang="ta">malai</term>, there must be a difference between the two.</note>,</l>
<l>– we'll go, rise – may your lifetime be excellent.</l>
<l>It is difficult to obtain an equivalent to [her] life</l>
<l rend="indent">when listening to the fur-eyed drum</l>
<l rend="indent">with resounding tones that possess the blackness of distress too, that</l>
<l rend="indent">was suffered, for [her] shame to be killed, by the ornament-hung bosom</l>
<l rend="indent4">of the little woman of tender nature, with narrow(?)<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">nalkūr</term> "poor" in connection with a waist certainly has to mean something like "narrow"?</note> waist,</l>
<l rend="indent4">bamboo shoulders [and] perfect jewels who is hidden on the side.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
